Step 1: To setup the Env 
    python -m venv venv
 Step 2: To activate the env 
    .\venv\Scripts\Activate

Step 3: to run the  jupyter code 
    pip install ipykernel

Step 4 : Installing packages 
    python -m pip install numpy
    python -m pip install pandas
    python -m pip install playwrightpython -m pip install path_to_project
